{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 348.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she comes and sits by the bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I say it out loud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About eight months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eight, nine months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Date-wise?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're somewhere now in 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My cousin, who is the oldest of us-- I mean, already in her late teens-- actually, I think, is the one who goes and is able, finally, to get us those passports, I think, through Sugihara, that Japanese--",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--transit visas so that we will be able to get into Russia as a jump-off point of getting out of that part of the world.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you, you can't get out of Europe anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People who got out earlier, who came, like, let's say-- you know, who went from Vienna to London by plane, all that is closed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All that has been now-- because of the war, World War II is raging.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the only way out will be through Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so she gets us transit visas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I think now there is more talk about hopefully getting to-- through Russia, then Japan, Canada, and then hopefully, the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if we can't get in the United States, we may end up having to go to South America, which is the two places people went to.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't physically remember leaving Vilnius.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't even tell you how we left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My guess is at that point-- by that point, we're traveling by train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is no longer the traveling by sled, hiding from the enemy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because so far, this is all still on the Russian control.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Shortly thereafter, the war will break out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Germans will take over Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That will be a very different story for the Jews who are there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we, actually, I think, leave by train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember getting to Moscow-- incredible experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
